column5: Hello Forum, was wondering about Old Oshawa marina access i heard that its federal land now as of May 2012 I have read and been told that there's an abundance of topwater strikers and was wondering how to get in there from the road. Thinking about heading there this week sometime.
what time do you want to go?  I'm in Whitby and ready to give it a go.  PM me if you want my cell # Geoff
